### Mongoose 

**Step-01** Mongoose Installation
> npm install mongoose --save

**Step-02** Import mongoose

```js
const mongoose = require(`mongoose`)
```
**Step-03** Connect with mongodb

```js
mongoose.connect('mongodb://localhost/shema', {userNewUrlParser: true});
```

